title: Cowdray Farm Shop Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Raw, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Based on the Cowdray Estate, cafe offers a variety of fresh organic juices, raw snacks, vegan and vegetarian dishes. Most fruit and veggies are local or organic. Try the vegan burger and the mezze plate which is vegetarian and can be made vegan.
